SedjPkOm81USde0j75S-9I4", "posted_on": {"day": 18, "month": 10, "year": 2024}, "text": "We\u2019re going back to our mountain roots with the new #MountainDew logo, leaning into the brands legacy with a fresh twist. This new visual identity was inspired by Mountain Dew\u2019s adventurous spirit, connecting today\u2019s generation with our brand\u2019s history of enjoying life outside and embracing the 'Do the Dew' spirit.\u200b", "total_likes": 1834}, {"article_link": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/pepsico_in-the-uk-were-stirring-the-pot-our-activity-7257417284992823297-obZ8", "image": null, "posted_on": {"day": 1, "month": 11, "year": 2024}, "text": "In the U.K. we\u2019re stirring the pot \u2013 our customer-favorite Quaker porridge pots are on the shelves in paper packaging that is easier to recycle with household paper products. Take a look how we\u2019re reducing 200 tonnes of virgin plastic packaging a year.", "total_likes": 375}, {"article_link": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/pepsico_national-coffee-day-activity-7246160773595430913-Ij3m", "image": null, "posted_on": {"day": 8, "month": 10, "year": 2024}, "text": "No better way to kick off #NationalCoffeeDay than by celebrating 30 years of innovation alongside Starbucks through the North American Coffee Partnership. Together, we\u2019ve helped define the ready-to-drink coffee experience, starting with the launch of Starbucks bottled Frappuccinos in 1996 and continuing to evolve with products inspired by fan-favorites from Starbucks caf\u00e9s.\u200b \n\nWe\u2019re proud of what we've achieved together, thank you to our teams who made it all possible \u2013 cheers!", "total_likes": 2062}, {"article_link": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/pepsico_curious-to-see-what-our-culture-can-offer-activity-7249063423290851328-38kK", "image": null, "posted_on": {"day": 8, "month": 10, "year": 2024}, "text": "Curious to see what our culture can offer through the eyes of our associates? Click here to experience how our people approach their work and relationships at PepsiCo: http://spr.ly/6047UpN0H", "total_likes": 154}], "follower_count": 8396230, "acquisitions": null, "exit_data": null, "extra": null, "funding_data": [], "categories": null, "customer_list": null}
